Title: Burooj Air

Description: Burooj Air is the first Saudi company licensed for drone cleaning services, offering innovative and eco-friendly solutions for high-rise facade cleaning, window cleaning, solar panel cleaning, and elevated asset maintenance. The project replaces traditional high-risk methods (lifts, scaffolding, facade climbers) with precision drone technology to improve safety, efficiency, and sustainability.

## Project Overview

This is a commercial website built with **Nuxt.js 2** (Vue.js framework) that serves as the official online presence for Burooj Air, a leading drone services company based in Saudi Arabia. The website showcases the company's services, team, gallery, and provides lead generation capabilities through integrated forms.

## Key Technologies

- **Framework**: Nuxt.js 2.15.8 (Vue.js 2.6.14)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 3.3.3 with custom SCSS
- **Internationalization**: Vue I18n (@nuxtjs/i18n) - English and Arabic support
- **Build Target**: Static site generation (SSG)
- **Deployment**: Static hosting (SSR disabled)
- **Additional Libraries**: 
  - Chart.js for data visualization
  - Vue Light Gallery for image galleries
  - Animate.css for animations
  - Flowbite for UI components

